    ns1:learningResultDescription "knowledge of the basic fabrication methods, structure and properties of nanomaterials and other forms of nanostructured hybrids"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000624/2025-26/RA16> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA16" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Knowledge and understanding of the electrical, optical, thermal and mechanical properties of materials"@es .

